# 🔍 PrivyShare (ShadowVault) — Comprehensive Project Audit Report

> **Date:** March 12, 2026  
> **Scope:** Full codebase review — frontend, smart contract, encryption, IPFS, wallet integration  
> **Files Reviewed:** 40+ files across `app/`, `components/`, `lib/`, `contracts/`, config files

