## 🎨 Section 6: UI/UX Improvements Needed

### Current UI Issues
1. **Bland color scheme** — All monochrome gray; no brand colors, gradients, or visual accents
2. **No file type icons** — Every file shows the same generic SVG badge
3. **No empty state illustrations** — Just plain text "No files"
4. **No confirmation dialogs** — Grant/revoke access happens with zero confirmation
5. **No toast notifications** — Success and error feedback are inline text only
6. **No mobile navigation** — Header nav breaks on small screens (no hamburger menu)
7. **No dark/light mode toggle** — Hardcoded dark mode only
8. **Settings page has no actual settings** — Only shows address and disconnect
9. **No "copy CID" button** — Owner needs to manually share CID with buyer
10. **Password strength indicator missing** — No feedback on encryption password quality

### Suggested Visual Enhancements
- Add gradient accents or brand color (e.g., Aleo teal/purple)
- Add subtle glow effects or glassmorphism for cards
- Skeleton loading states instead of text "Loading..."
- Animated success/error toasts (e.g., using `sonner` or `react-hot-toast`)
- File type detection (show 📄 PDF, 🖼️ Image, 📊 Spreadsheet icons)
- Progress stepper during upload flow (Encrypt → Upload → Register)

