9. **Add Aleo address validation** before submitting transactions
10. **Add React Error Boundary** component
11. **Add metadata backup** to IPFS (encrypted metadata file)
12. **Add loading skeletons** and toast notifications
13. **Add confirmation dialogs** for grant/revoke access

### 🟢 Priority 3 — Polish & Production Quality

14. **Create shared authenticated layout** (nested Next.js layout)
15. **Remove unused `ipfs-http-client`** dependency
16. **Add search/filter/pagination** to marketplace
17. **Add transaction history** page
18. **Add file previews/thumbnails**
19. **Mobile-responsive header** with hamburger menu
20. **Add unit tests** for crypto, encoding, and upload modules
21. **Set up CI/CD** (GitHub Actions)
22. **Add `.env` validation** at startup (zod schema)

